(add 1 2 3 4 5)                         ; => 15"))))
        (article :class "almighty-section"
          (h4 :id "mixing-lambda-list-keywords" :class "almighty-section-title"
            "Mixing lambda list keywords")
          (p :class "almighty-book-paragraph"
            "As a general rule, you don't want to mix"
            (code
              "&optional")
            "and"
            (code
              "&key")
            "parameters.")
