                                                                (article :class "almighty-section"
                                                                  (h2 :id "stickers" :class "almighty-section-title"
                                                                    "STICKERS")
                                                                  (p :class "almighty-book-paragraph"
                                                                    "Where Sly's debugging capabilities really shine is with"
                                                                    (code
                                                                      "stickers")
                                                                    ". Stickers are basically a replacement for"
                                                                    (code
                                                                      "print")
                                                                    "and"
                                                                    (code
                                                                      "break")
                                                                    "functions")
                                                                  (article :class "almighty-section"
                                                                    (h3 :id "sly-stickers-dwim" :class "almighty-section-title"
                                                                      "=sly-stickers-dwim=")
                                                                    (p :class "almighty-book-paragraph"
                                                                      "Let's say we have the following code:")
                                                                    (figure :class "almighty-code-block"
                                                                      (pre
                                                                        (code :class "almighty-src almighty-src-lisp"
                                                                          "(defun do-some-math (num)
  (/ (+ num (* num num num) (- num 10 num)) 7))
(do-some-math 9)")))
                                                                    (p :class "almighty-book-paragraph"
                                                                      "And you're thinking, \"Hmm, I wonder what the result of that addition was?\"")
                                                                    (p :class "almighty-book-paragraph"
                                                                      "You could wrap it in"
                                                                      (code
                                                                        "print")
                                                                      ". Or you could use a sticker. Highlight the opening parenthesis of the addition form then use"
                                                                      (code
                                                                        "sly-stickers-dwim")
                                                                      "via"
                                                                      (code
                                                                        "C-c C-s C-s")
                                                                      "or"
                                                                      (code
                                                                        "SPC m s s")
                                                                      "to place a sticker on it. After placing the sticker, you need to recompile the function ("
                                                                      (code
                                                                        "C-c C-c")
                                                                      ") to \"arm\" the sticker."))
                                                                  (article :class "almighty-section"
                                                                    (h3 :id "sly-stickers-replay" :class "almighty-section-title"
                                                                      "=sly-stickers-replay=")
                                                                    (p :class "almighty-book-paragraph"
                                                                      "With the sticker armed, when you run the function, the return value of the form you placed the sticker on will be recorded. You can view the recording with"
                                                                      (code
                                                                        "sly-stickers-replay")
                                                                      "using"
                                                                      (code
                                                                        "C-c C-s C-r")
                                                                      "or"
                                                                      (code
                                                                        "SPC m s r")
                                                                      "."))
                                                                  (article :class "almighty-section"
