                                                                    (p :class "almighty-book-paragraph"
                                                                      (code
                                                                        ":nicknames")
                                                                      "defines what other package name qualifiers you can use besides"
                                                                      (code
                                                                        "hunchentoot")
                                                                      ". That means that Hunchentoot itself provides you the ability to use"
                                                                      (code
                                                                        "(tbnl:*acceptor*)")
                                                                      "if you want. Useful for allowing users to use a smaller package name qualifier on their symbols.")
                                                                    (p :class "almighty-book-paragraph"
                                                                      "Hunchentoot uses"
