                                                                    (p :class "almighty-book-paragraph"
                                                                      "The first thing you'll notice is that the definition is short. The dependencies only include...another file in the system? And there are no"
                                                                      (code
                                                                        ":components")
                                                                      "! To investigate, let's look in the \"utopian/main\"... file? Package? System?")
                                                                    (p :class "almighty-book-paragraph"
                                                                      "It's found in"
                                                                      (code
                                                                        "src/main.lisp")
                                                                      ":")
