(in-package #:utopian)")))
                                                                    (p :class "almighty-book-paragraph"
                                                                      "We already saw"
                                                                      (code
                                                                        ":nicknames")
                                                                      "in the Hunchentoot"
                                                                      (code
                                                                        "packages.lisp")
                                                                      "file."
                                                                      (code
                                                                        ":mix-reexport")
                                                                      "is like"
                                                                      (code
                                                                        ":use-reexport")
                                                                      "that we saw in Mito, except that it will inherit"
                                                                      (i
                                                                        "all")
                                                                      "symbols, exported and not, from the packages that follow into the current package. Every single symbol from those six packages above are going to be inherited into the"
                                                                      (code
                                                                        "#:utopian")
                                                                      "package.")
                                                                    (p :class "almighty-book-paragraph"
