  :pathname \"src\"
  :depends-on (\"almighty/main\"))")))
                                                                    (p :class "almighty-book-paragraph"
                                                                      "Notice here that the system is named"
                                                                      (code
                                                                        "almighty")
                                                                      ", and that the package/system in"
                                                                      (code
                                                                        ":depends-on")
                                                                      "begins with"
                                                                      (code
                                                                        "almighty")
                                                                      ". The entry-point and all subsequent packages in your package-inferred-system must begin with"
                                                                      (code
                                                                        "almighty")
                                                                      ".")
                                                                    (p :class "almighty-book-paragraph"
                                                                      "Notice also that"
                                                                      (code
                                                                        ":pathname")
                                                                      "is set. The tree view of this project looks like this:")
                                                                    (figure :class "almighty-code-block"
                                                                      (pre
                                                                        (code :class "almighty-src almighty-src-lisp"
